{"tid":1950565,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"寰宇疫情後開戲 劉德華演《A380》城城古仔拍《掃毒3》","createTime":"2020-03-30T11:48:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T10:59:51.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"01bca49264fe19629af5345a97c66b7b4a8e9c86","tid":1950565,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T11:48:55.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情仍然在全球肆虐，中港兩地影視製作近乎停頓，不過寰宇電影公司也準備在疫情過後會開拍兩部過億元製作的電影，一部是劉德華主演的飛機空難片《A380》，以及拍《掃毒3》，第一集是由古天樂、劉青雲和張家輝主演，第二部《掃毒2天地對決》因張家輝臨時要加片酬，搞到老闆一氣之下變陣，改由劉德華、古天樂和苗僑偉演出，至於今年暑假後開拍的《掃毒3》，傳聞又變組合，由郭富城、古仔和劉青雲主演。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》今日搵寰宇老闆林小明，他證實今年確實有計劃開拍這兩部電影，已經開始在籌備，他表示：「《掃毒3》我係想轉吓人做，咁樣觀眾先會有新鮮感，初步我係好想搵城城、古仔同青雲一齊拍第3集，等劇本出嚟後，再搵佢哋傾，睇佢哋演唔演啦！而華仔我就同佢講過拍飛機空難片《A380》，佢初步係有興趣嘅！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200330/large/1585561156_c8f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200330%2Flarge%2F1585561156_c8f9.jpg&h=f573eba9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200330/N4O2VJSV4MOEE4WM7GWG4BRMUE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200330%2FN4O2VJSV4MOEE4WM7GWG4BRMUE%2F&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2Rn9kyGvuUmJUtyTBy059fc%3D&h=368ed316\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200330%2FN4O2VJSV4MOEE4WM7GWG4BRMUE%2F&h=89a66284\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200330/N4O2VJSV4MOEE4WM7GWG4BRMUE/</a><br />\n<br />\n拍完到底有冇人睇架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baa441ffd171878ab2b328b47f1a72e1cbad4973","tid":1950565,"uid":312363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T11:51:05.000Z","msg":"不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /